snippet.title: Johnny Turbo's Arcade: Wizard Fire Trailer for Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Johnny Turbo's Arcade: Wizard Fire available NOW!

Get it here: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/johnny-turbos-arcade-wizard-fire-switch

Wizard Fire is the sequel to the original hit 90’s classic arcade game, Gate of Doom/Dark Seal, with 2-player Co-Op play action. Choose a hero from the cast of characters and lead them on a quest to save the kingdom. Collect experience points by stopping your foes, and use them to gain magic spells.

Who will save us from these heralds of darkness? Come one, come all and hear the tale of the Valiant Knights of the Wizard Fire.
